		text		: "1\n00:00:22,646 --> 00:00:27,317\nHi there! I’m Anna and I live in Washington, D.C.\n\n2\n00:00:27,419 --> 00:00:31,250\nEvery day I learn more about this great city.\n\n3\n00:00:31,456 --> 00:00:35,989\nPeople in Washington like to work out!\n\n4\n00:00:36,093 --> 00:00:40,839\nOh, hi, Pete. How’s it going?\n\n5\n00:00:40,950 --> 00:00:43,566\nHi, Anna. It’s going great.\n\n6\n00:00:43,971 --> 00:00:46,087\nHow’s it going with you?\n\n7\n00:00:46,195 --> 00:00:48,006\nThings are awesome!\n\n8\n00:00:48,156 --> 00:00:51,583\nPete, I want to work out.\n\n9\n00:00:51,792 --> 00:00:53,000\nWhere is the gym?\n\n10\n00:00:53,100 --> 00:00:55,821\nThe gym is across from the lounge.\n\n11\n00:00:55,922 --> 00:00:58,948\nIt’s next to the mailroom.\n\n12\n00:00:59,056 --> 00:01:00,164\nGo that way.\n\n13\n00:01:00,264 --> 00:01:01,474\nThanks, Pete!\n\n14\n00:01:02,410 --> 00:01:07,648\nNo, Anna! Not that way! Go that way!\n\n15\n00:01:33,821 --> 00:01:35,655\nOh, Pete.\n\n16\n00:01:35,968 --> 00:01:39,005\nThis is not the gym.\n\n17\n00:01:39,206 --> 00:01:41,015\nThat’s right, Anna.\n\n18\n00:01:41,239 --> 00:01:44,061\nThis is the mailroom.\n\n19\n00:01:44,161 --> 00:01:47,893\nThe gym is across from … what?\n\n20\n00:01:47,998 --> 00:01:50,918\nThe gym is across from the lounge.\n\n21\n00:01:50,918 --> 00:01:54,253\nAcross from the lounge.\n\n22\n00:01:54,564 --> 00:01:56,476\nRight. Thanks!\n\n23\n00:02:13,125 --> 00:02:17,074\nPete! This is not the gym!\n\n24\n00:02:17,274 --> 00:02:23,515\nThe gym is across from the lounge.\n\n25\n00:02:23,626 --> 00:02:27,351\nIt is behind the lobby.\n\n26\n00:02:27,459 --> 00:02:32,394\nRight. Right. See you.\n\n27\n00:02:32,509 --> 00:02:36,433\nSee you, Anna!\n\n28\n00:02:36,642 --> 00:02:38,754\nSee you.\n\n29\n00:02:38,863 --> 00:02:42,790\nSee you, Anna.\n\n30\n00:03:07,248 --> 00:03:09,261\nThis is not the gym.\n\n31\n00:03:10,068 --> 00:03:14,294\nThis is a parking garage.\n\n32\n00:03:14,404 --> 00:03:19,640\nHello? Pete?\n\n33\n00:03:31,251 --> 00:03:34,699\nThis is not a gym.\n\n34\n00:03:34,801 --> 00:03:37,919\nThis is a rooftop.\n\n35\n00:03:43,726 --> 00:03:46,144\nPete!\n\n36\n00:03:47,653 --> 00:03:50,776\nPete?\n\n37\n00:03:50,983 --> 00:03:53,097\nI want to work out too!\n\n38\n00:03:53,399 --> 00:03:54,910\nJoin me!\n\n39\n00:03:55,037 --> 00:03:58,158\nI’m good.",
