		title		: "Lesson 22: Next Summer...",
		text		: "1\n00:00:16,227 --> 00:00:19,551\nWashington, D.C. has four seasons:\n\n2\n00:00:19,855 --> 00:00:23,680\nwinter, spring, summer and autumn or fall.\n\n3\n00:00:24,295 --> 00:00:28,723\nMy favorite season is summer because of summer vacation!\n\n4\n00:00:29,026 --> 00:00:35,267\nHey, that will be a great subject for my new work assignment\n\n5\n00:00:35,568 --> 00:00:36,677\nthe children’s show.\n\n6\n00:00:36,878 --> 00:00:42,215\nI can teach what families in the U.S. do during summer vacation.\n\n7\n00:00:43,853 --> 00:00:47,584\nToday, I’m planning the show with Amelia.\n\n8\n00:00:48,095 --> 00:00:50,607\nThis is the first time we are working together.\n\n9\n00:00:51,415 --> 00:00:53,527\nI hope we can work well together.\n\n10\n00:00:54,946 --> 00:00:56,069\nHi, Amelia!\n\n11\n00:00:56,271 --> 00:00:57,091\nHi, Anna!\n\n12\n00:00:58,893 --> 00:01:02,719\nSo, what are we going to talk about on the first show?\n\n13\n00:01:02,883 --> 00:01:05,597\nI want to talk about summer vacation.\n\n14\n00:01:05,999 --> 00:01:07,307\nThat will be fun!\n\n15\n00:01:07,619 --> 00:01:09,532\nAre you going on vacation this summer?\n\n16\n00:01:09,833 --> 00:01:12,146\nNo. This summer I am too busy.\n\n17\n00:01:12,463 --> 00:01:14,374\nThat’s too bad.\n\n18\n00:01:14,491 --> 00:01:15,404\nIt’s okay.\n\n19\n00:01:15,519 --> 00:01:17,236\nI can go on vacation next summer.\n\n20\n00:01:17,761 --> 00:01:19,974\nThis show will be a lot of fun too!\n\n21\n00:01:52,687 --> 00:01:55,204\nSo, Anna, what’s the plan for the show?\n\n22\n00:01:55,404 --> 00:01:58,232\nFirst, we’re going to introduce the subject.\n\n23\n00:01:58,549 --> 00:02:02,476\nThen we can show pictures and video.\n\n24\n00:02:02,690 --> 00:02:04,403\nWe can show tons of video!\n\n25\n00:02:04,814 --> 00:02:08,941\nRight! We can interview children and have guests, too.\n\n26\n00:02:09,374 --> 00:02:11,588\nKids can ask us questions.\n\n27\n00:02:11,991 --> 00:02:13,197\nGreat idea!\n\n28\n00:02:13,905 --> 00:02:18,435\nFinally, we can read the questions and tell them where to learn more.\n\n29\n00:02:18,854 --> 00:02:20,464\nOkay, let’s try it!\n\n30\n00:02:20,878 --> 00:02:21,682\nLet’s do it!\n\n31\n00:03:03,462 --> 00:03:05,071\nHi there!\n\n32\n00:03:05,173 --> 00:03:06,398\nAnd welcome to …\n\n33\n00:03:08,140 --> 00:03:08,844\nAmelia,\n\n34\n00:03:08,946 --> 00:03:10,458\nwe don’t have a name for the show.\n\n35\n00:03:10,961 --> 00:03:12,473\nWe’ll think of a name later.\n\n36\n00:03:12,775 --> 00:03:14,999\nFor now, we'll call it “The Show.”\n\n37\n00:03:15,300 --> 00:03:16,205\nGreat.\n\n38\n00:03:17,312 --> 00:03:19,830\nHi there! And welcome to “The Show.”\n\n39\n00:03:20,652 --> 00:03:23,988\nToday we are going to take you on a summer vacation!\n\n40\n00:03:24,509 --> 00:03:27,731\nYou will see popular things to do on vacation!\n\n41\n00:03:28,137 --> 00:03:29,849\nOne is camping.\n\n42\n00:03:30,272 --> 00:03:34,800\nWhen you go camping, you cook, sleep and play outdoors!\n\n43\n00:03:35,208 --> 00:03:39,535\nWhen I go camping, Anna, I like to go hiking and fishing.\n\n44\n00:03:39,749 --> 00:03:41,261\nMe, too.\n\n45\n00:03:41,562 --> 00:03:43,977\nThose are fun things to do when you go camping!\n\n46\n00:03:44,179 --> 00:03:46,193\nThese people are hiking.\n\n47\n00:03:46,529 --> 00:03:50,557\nOkay, let’s talk about the next vacation.\n\n48\n00:03:50,759 --> 00:03:55,698\nAnother popular summer vacation is going to an amusement park.\n\n49\n00:03:56,002 --> 00:04:01,037\nAt an amusement park, you go on rides and eat lots of fun food!\n\n50\n00:04:01,539 --> 00:04:03,353\nI love cotton candy … !\n\n51\n00:04:03,654 --> 00:04:05,781\nand rollercoasters!\n\n52\n00:04:06,689 --> 00:04:08,702\nThis show is going to be a lot of fun.\n\n53\n00:04:09,111 --> 00:04:10,019\nI know!\n\n54\n00:04:10,639 --> 00:04:12,975\nThis is riding a rollercoaster!\n\n55\n00:04:13,314 --> 00:04:19,555\nWhoooo! What is the last vacation?\n\n56\n00:04:20,188 --> 00:04:26,330\nOne of the most popular vacations is … going to the beach!\n\n57\n00:04:26,449 --> 00:04:28,368\nI love the beach!\n\n58\n00:04:28,781 --> 00:04:32,507\nWhen I see that blue ocean,\n\n59\n00:04:32,723 --> 00:04:37,970\nI want to leave Washington, D.C. immediately and go to the beach!\n\n60\n00:04:41,776 --> 00:04:43,388\nMaybe next summer.\n\n61\n00:04:43,994 --> 00:04:47,011\nBut right now, it’s time to work!\n\n62\n00:04:47,417 --> 00:04:49,947\nRight. Until next time ...",
