		title		: "Lesson 23: What Do You Want?",
		text		: "1\n00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:17,640\nHi, there!\n\n2\n00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:21,660\nWashington, D.C. has great food from all over the world.\n\n3\n00:00:21,660 --> 00:00:21,840\nToday I’m having lunch with my boss.\nWashington, D.C. has great food from all over the world.\n\n4\n00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:24,760\nToday I’m having lunch with my boss.\n\n5\n00:00:24,760 --> 00:00:24,880\nMs. Weaver says we’re going on a trip around the world.\nToday I’m having lunch with my boss.\n\n6\n00:00:24,880 --> 00:00:29,160\nMs. Weaver says we’re going on a trip around the world.\n\n7\n00:00:29,160 --> 00:00:29,400\nBut she knows I only have an hour for lunch! Silly woman.\nMs. Weaver says we’re going on a trip around the world.\n\n8\n00:00:29,400 --> 00:00:34,880\nBut she knows I only have an hour for lunch! Silly woman.\n\n9\n00:00:35,400 --> 00:00:36,766\nHi, Anna!\n\n10\n00:00:36,830 --> 00:00:37,937\nHi Jonathan!\n\n11\n00:00:38,097 --> 00:00:42,400\nHey, we are meeting Ms. Weaver for lunch at noon, aren’t we?\n\n12\n00:00:42,435 --> 00:00:43,000\nYes.\n\n13\n00:00:43,033 --> 00:00:44,700\nWhat time is it now?\n\n14\n00:00:44,733 --> 00:00:46,033\n11:50.\n\n15\n00:00:46,071 --> 00:00:50,000\n11:50! We have to go!\n\n16\n00:01:16,100 --> 00:01:19,102\nSo, where is this world food restaurant?\n\n17\n00:01:19,166 --> 00:01:21,666\nWe’re not eating at a restaurant.\n\n18\n00:01:22,035 --> 00:01:23,911\nWhere are we eating?\n\n19\n00:01:24,168 --> 00:01:26,728\nWe are eating at ... food trucks!\n\n20\n00:01:26,728 --> 00:01:28,728\nFood trucks … awesome!\n\n21\n00:01:28,728 --> 00:01:30,177\nWhat’s a food truck?\n\n22\n00:01:30,177 --> 00:01:32,177\nThese are food trucks!\n\n23\n00:01:55,813 --> 00:01:59,662\nOkay, Jonathan, you will buy the first dish.\n\n24\n00:01:59,662 --> 00:02:02,924\nHere is $10. Surprise us!\n\n25\n00:02:02,924 --> 00:02:05,973\nOkay, I’ll be back in 15 minutes.\n\n26\n00:02:08,204 --> 00:02:10,320\nWhat country do I want to visit?\n\n27\n00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:13,733\nAnna, you pick the second country.\n\n28\n00:02:14,666 --> 00:02:16,853\nHere is $10.\n\n29\n00:02:16,853 --> 00:02:18,853\nI want chicken.\n\n30\n00:02:19,075 --> 00:02:22,684\nThe food truck, over there, has great chicken.\n\n31\n00:02:22,684 --> 00:02:24,684\nAwesome!\n\n32\n00:02:25,893 --> 00:02:29,635\nAfter you buy your food, meet me here.\n\n33\n00:02:31,795 --> 00:02:33,928\nExcuse me, I’ll have the shrimp.\n\n34\n00:02:35,484 --> 00:02:37,973\nOh, you’re out of shrimp.\n\n35\n00:02:38,488 --> 00:02:41,235\nOkay, I’ll have the beef then.\n\n36\n00:02:41,555 --> 00:02:43,928\nHello. I want the chicken dish.\n\n37\n00:02:44,062 --> 00:02:45,128\nWe're out of chicken.\n\n38\n00:02:45,297 --> 00:02:46,506\nYou're out of chicken.\n\n39\n00:02:46,515 --> 00:02:46,835\nYep.\n\n40\n00:02:47,288 --> 00:02:48,800\nI’ll try another food truck.\n\n41\n00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:49,235\nThanks!\n\n42\n00:02:49,270 --> 00:02:50,497\nYou're welcome.\n\n43\n00:03:13,650 --> 00:03:16,257\nOkay, here is your change.\n\n44\n00:03:16,622 --> 00:03:18,640\nThe dish is $7.\n\n45\n00:03:18,693 --> 00:03:24,764\nSo, here is 1, 2, 3 dollars back from your 10.\n\n46\n00:03:24,835 --> 00:03:25,715\nGreat.\n\n47\n00:03:26,124 --> 00:03:28,337\nWhere’s Anna?\n\n48\n00:03:30,675 --> 00:03:35,511\nIs she dancing by that food truck?\n\n49\n00:03:35,626 --> 00:03:38,595\nYes. Yes, she is.\n\n50\n00:03:42,924 --> 00:03:45,306\nMs. Weaver, here is your change.\n\n51\n00:03:45,306 --> 00:03:51,004\nThe dish costs $5. So - $5 back.\n\n52\n00:03:51,004 --> 00:03:54,248\nThanks, Anna. But where is the food?\n\n53\n00:03:54,462 --> 00:03:56,968\nI’m eating it.\n\n54\n00:03:56,968 --> 00:04:02,320\nThe Peruvian chicken is delicious! Try some!\n\n55\n00:04:34,897 --> 00:04:37,991\nWell, we still have $8!\n\n56\n00:04:37,991 --> 00:04:39,991\nWhat do you want now?\n\n57\n00:04:39,991 --> 00:04:41,991\nWe can buy dessert!\n\n58\n00:04:42,488 --> 00:04:44,702\nI’ll buy dessert.\n\n59\n00:04:46,213 --> 00:04:50,186\nIn Washington, D.C., you can travel around the world …\n\n60\n00:04:50,275 --> 00:04:54,035\nwith food trucks! And it does not cost a lot.\n\n61\n00:04:54,035 --> 00:04:56,035\nUntil next time!",
