		title		: "Lesson 28: I Passed It!",
		text		: "1\n00:00:16,547 --> 00:00:17,716\nHello!\n\n2\n00:00:17,846 --> 00:00:19,987\nThis is my driver’s license!\nGuess what this is? \n\n3\n00:00:19,987 --> 00:00:22,510\nThis is my driver’s license!\n\n4\n00:00:22,510 --> 00:00:24,861\nI passed my driving test!\n\n5\n00:00:24,861 --> 00:00:30,898\nToday, I rented a car so I can drive around Washington, D.C.\n\n6\n00:00:30,898 --> 00:00:34,141\nYou can see more of the city this way.\n\n7\n00:00:34,141 --> 00:00:36,141\nMarsha!\n\n8\n00:00:37,070 --> 00:00:40,640\nAnna, did you get your driver’s license?\n\n9\n00:00:40,640 --> 00:00:42,344\nI did! \n\n10\n00:00:42,340 --> 00:00:45,396\nBut it was not easy.\n\n11\n00:00:45,396 --> 00:00:47,969\nWhy? What happened?\n\n12\n00:00:47,969 --> 00:00:52,818\nWell, you know, I can drive farm equipment really well.\n\n13\n00:00:56,535 --> 00:01:01,593\nBut I was really nervous driving in Washington, D.C. traffic!\n\n14\n00:01:01,590 --> 00:01:04,769\nDid you pass the test the first time?\n\n15\n00:01:05,126 --> 00:01:08,615\nWell…no.\n\n16\n00:01:08,615 --> 00:01:11,273\nBut I did pass the second time.\n\n17\n00:01:33,963 --> 00:01:36,843\nWhat happened during the first test?\n\n18\n00:01:37,507 --> 00:01:39,630\nIt started fine.\n\n19\n00:01:45,095 --> 00:01:50,043\nOkay … Anna. Is your seatbelt buckled?\n\n20\n00:01:50,043 --> 00:01:52,043\nYes, sir!\n\n21\n00:01:54,104 --> 00:01:57,366\nGreat. Please start the car.\n\n22\n00:01:57,366 --> 00:02:00,024\n(to herself) Okay, Anna, start the car.\n\n23\n00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:04,092\nI Started the car.\n\n24\n00:02:05,950 --> 00:02:06,006\nGood job, Anna.\n\n25\n00:02:06,006 --> 00:02:08,252\nWhy are you talking to yourself?\nGood job, Anna.\n\n26\n00:02:08,252 --> 00:02:10,252\nI am a little nervous.\nGood job, Anna.\n\n27\n00:02:10,252 --> 00:02:12,916\nWhen I’m nervous, I talk to myself.\nGood job, Anna.\n\n28\n00:02:12,916 --> 00:02:13,249\nGood job, Anna.\n\n29\n00:02:13,415 --> 00:02:17,415\nYou don't need to be nervous.\n\n30\n00:02:17,741 --> 00:02:20,486\nListen to that engine!\n\n31\n00:02:23,446 --> 00:02:27,440\nPlease, stop pushing the gas pedal!\n\n32\n00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:29,440\nSorry.\n\n33\n00:02:31,901 --> 00:02:34,320\nOkay, when you are ready, turn.\n\n34\n00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:35,089\nGreat!\n\n35\n00:02:35,089 --> 00:02:37,692\nNot now! You almost hit that car!\n\n36\n00:02:37,692 --> 00:02:39,027\nYou said “turn!”\n\n37\n00:02:39,020 --> 00:02:39,852\nLook first!\n\n38\n00:02:39,852 --> 00:02:41,852\nThere were cars in the street.\n\n39\n00:02:41,852 --> 00:02:43,852\nPlease don’t yell at me!\n\n40\n00:02:43,852 --> 00:02:45,852\nI’m sorry!\n\n41\n00:02:45,852 --> 00:02:46,769\nI was afraid.\n\n42\n00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:48,596\nYou were yelling.\n\n43\n00:02:48,590 --> 00:02:52,073\nLook out for that car! Brake! Brake!! Ahhh!\n\n44\n00:02:53,372 --> 00:02:55,667\nWhy is everyone honking at us?\n\n45\n00:02:55,667 --> 00:02:57,667\nYou were driving too slow!\n\n46\n00:02:57,667 --> 00:02:59,926\nAnna, stay on the street!\n\n47\n00:03:01,538 --> 00:03:03,846\nHands on the wheel, Anna.\n\n48\n00:03:03,846 --> 00:03:06,295\nWhat’s that sound?\n\n49\n00:03:07,803 --> 00:03:11,070\nThat, Anna, is the police.\n\n50\n00:03:37,390 --> 00:03:39,206\nThat sounds awful.\n\n51\n00:03:39,206 --> 00:03:42,104\nYes, it did not go well.\n\n52\n00:03:42,104 --> 00:03:45,913\nBut, I practiced and passed the second time!\n\n53\n00:03:45,913 --> 00:03:52,283\nDo you know where you want to take your first drive in Washington, D.C.?\n\n54\n00:03:52,283 --> 00:03:54,935\nYes! Let’s go!\n\n55\n00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:10,670\nThere it is … the White House!\n\n56\n00:04:10,996 --> 00:04:18,301\nAnna, you do know you can’t drive up to the White House, don’t you?\n\n57\n00:04:18,301 --> 00:04:22,190\nYes. No. I didn’t know.\n\n58\n00:04:22,190 --> 00:04:24,190\nI guess we walk from here!\n\n59\n00:04:32,264 --> 00:04:36,141\nSometimes you can see more of Washington, D.C. in a car.\n\n60\n00:04:36,141 --> 00:04:38,535\nIf you want to see the White House,\n\n61\n00:04:38,547 --> 00:04:40,160\nyou need to walk.\n\n62\n00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,889\nUntil next time … !",
